its first production venture. The Friday Film House won 7 of the Kerala State Film Awards in various fields in 2014. On January 3, 2017, the founders had a quarrel with each other in their office after which Sandra Thomas filed a case against Vijay Babu. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/entertainment/actor-vijay-babu-accused-of-assaulting-producer-sandra-thomas-how-their-friendship-soured-3187136.html|title=Actor Vijay Babu accused of assaulting producer Sandra Thomas: How their friendship soured|accessdate=4 January 2017}}</ref> Later both declared that it was a misunderstanding and that Sandra had taken a break from the industry. Subsequently the stake of Sandra in the firm was excluded and the possession solely acquired by Vijay Babu.\n\n== Films ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Key\n| style=\"background:#ffc;\"| {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Director\n!class=unsortable| Notes\n!class=unsortable| Ref.\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Friday (Malayalam film)|Friday]]'' || Production<br />Distribution || [[Lijin Jose]] || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/friday-another-with-multi-narrative-aspect/259148-71-210.html|title=Friday: Another with multi narrative aspect}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Zachariayude Garbhinikal]]'' || Production || [[Aneesh Anwar]] || || <ref name=\"Zach\">{{cite web|url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/mollywood/050619/friday-film-house-to-produce-gangs-of-bandadukka.html|title=Friday Film House to produce Gangs of Bandadukka|work=[[Deccan Chronicle]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Philips and the Monkey Pen]]'' || Production<br />Distribution || [[Rojin Thomas]]<br />Shanil Muhammed || Kerala State Film Award for Best Children's Film Director <br /> Kerala State Film Award for Best Child Artist - [[Sanoop Santhosh]] <br /> Kerala State Film Award for Best Children's Film <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowrunning.com/movie/12271/malayalam/philips-and-the-monkey-pen/index.htm |title=Philips and the Monkey Pen Malayalam Movie - Preview, Trailers, Gallery, Review, Events, Synopsis |publisher=Nowrunning.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thecinenews.com/2013/11/philips-and-monkey-pen-movie-review.html |title=What got special on'Philips & the Monkey Pen' : Miracles never ends on M'Town |publisher=The Cine News |date= |accessdate=November 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110085732/http://www.thecinenews.com/2013/11/philips-and-monkey-pen-movie-review.html |archive-date=10 November 2013 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"tikk\">{{cite web|url=http://www.tikkview.com/movies/5110-philips-and-the-monkey-pen |title=Philips and the Monkey Pen - Find what you like |publisher=tikkview |date=2012-02-24 |accessdate=2013-11-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/malayalam-film-philips--the-monkey-pen-releases-today-south/20131107.htm |title=Malayalam film Philips & the Monkey Pen releases today - Rediff.com Movies |publisher=Rediff.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-07}}</ref> || <ref name=\"Zach\" />\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Peruchazhi]]'' || Production<br />Distribution || [[Arun Vaidyanathan]] ||  || <ref name=\"Founder\" />\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Aadu (film)|Aadu Oru Bheegara Jeevi Aanu]]'' || Production<br />Distribution || [[Midhun Manuel Thomas]] ||  || <ref name=\"Founder\" />\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Adi Kapyare Kootamani]]'' || Production<br />Distribution || John Varghese ||  || <ref name=\"Founder\" />\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Theri (film)|Theri]]'' || Distribution || [[Atlee (director)|Atlee]] || || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/theris-kerala-theatrical-rights-sold-to-carnival-motion-pictures-and-friday-film-house.html|title=Theri's Kerala theatrical rights sold|work=Behindwoods}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Mudhugauv]